<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Positive" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Positive,</orth> certain, unquestionable: <emph>it is as p. as</emph> <cit><quote>the earth is firm,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 2, 49</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>'tis p. 'gainst all exceptions,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.2.25" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 2, 25</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Patroclus is a fool p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 70</bibl></cit> (== unconditional).
